Method 🍔: 
Spread some butter on your buns and toast your buns on a medium hot pan til golden. Karaage Chicken 🥢 
Chicken thigh 
1 tbs ginger 
1 tbs garlic 
2 tbs soy sauce 
2 tbs flour 
1 egg 
1 cornflour 

Method 🥢: 
Cut the chicken into bite size pieces and marinate with the ginger, garlic, soy sauce. Add the flour and egg and mix well. In another plate add the cornflour and cover the marinated chicken in it well. Fry for 1 minute and take it out for 30 seconds, repeat 3x for crispy chicken!
